Return to Paradise;;74;;71;;R;;Lewis (Joaquin Phoenix), Sheriff (Vince Vaughn) and Tony (David Conrad) are three friends vacationing in Malaysia. Sheriff and Tony eventually leave to pursue careers in New York, but Lewis stays behind to work with orangutans. Two years later, Sheriff and Tony learn that, because of their past actions, Lewis has been arrested for drug possession. With Lewis facing a death sentence, the friends are left with a difficult decision: return to Malaysia and split Lewis' sentence, or let him die.;;Drama;;Joseph Ruben;;1998;;Vince Vaughn,Anne Heche,Joaquin Phoenix,David Conrad,Vera Farmiga,Nick Sandow,Jada Pinkett Smith,Richard Chang;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1083688-return_to_paradise